562
00:54:50.328 --> 00:54:52.008
Ne. ne!

563
00:54:53.381 --> 00:54:54.600
Moja djeca.
Neytiri.

564
00:54:54.625 --> 00:54:56.316
Moja djeca!
Smiri se!

565
00:54:56.341 --> 00:54:58.140
Smiri se.
Moja djeca.

566
00:54:58.750 --> 00:55:01.335
Moja djeca.
Gdje su?

567
00:55:02.889 --> 00:55:03.889
Gdje su?

568
