Tuk!

616
00:58:58.320 --> 00:58:59.985
Tuk.
Kiri.

617
00:59:00.069 --> 00:59:01.264
Lo'ak.

618
00:59:04.096 --> 00:59:06.873
Jake.
Jesi li dobro?

619
00:59:07.093 --> 00:59:10.090
U redu je.
Na sigurnom si.

620
00:59:11.103 --> 00:59:12.353
